{"tid":1005480,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] メガミラ 奇蹟女神力 - 地雷社手遊新作","createTime":"2019-02-02T09:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T20:43:13.000Z","uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed26e1e8f35e7aa06f6e6df3f26fdaf56267a4b","tid":1005480,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XMTEfKVw_nc/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FXMTEfKVw_nc%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=c509cab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://megamiracle-force.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegamiracle-force.com%2F&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2VcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=76072ec4\" target=\"_blank\">https://megamiracle-force.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/WIKI/83/00363383.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FWIKI%2F83%2F00363383.JPG&h=5d7a7ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　眾多種族存在的廣大世界『超次元』。一道神奇的流星，劃過西方大陸「普拉涅迪努（プラネテューヌ）」的藍天。如流星般墜落普拉涅迪努近郊硬生生插在地上的，正是本作主角正是玩家您。剛回復意識的玩家面前，出現自稱「涅普迪努」和「克羅媧兒」的兩名少女。在失去的記憶中隱藏的真相、無法化身女神的守護女神、等待在前方的因果之戰。還有這名叫『超次元』的世界。<br />\n <br />\n　　眾多思念交錯、追尋各自期望的未來，冒險之旅就此展開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/WIKI/79/00363379.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FWIKI%2F79%2F00363379.JPG&h=d750d4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　本作為 Idea Factory 集團 25 周年紀念企劃作品。遊戲中將集合 Compile Heart 旗下《戰機少女》系列、《極限凸騎》系列、《妖精劍士 f》系列等作，以及 Idea Factory 旗下《聖魔戰記》系列、《渾沌世代》系列等作的角色，促成一款跨界遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n　　本作為一款簡單卻深奧，戰略模擬 RPG，戰鬥會在橫 7 縱 5 的場地上進行。對場地上的角色下指令，運用遠距離攻擊、貫穿攻擊、擊飛等不同攻擊方式和技能，擊倒敵方隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n　　各作品的插圖都會化作「連結卡（リンクカード）」於本作登場。透過主角身上的不可思議力量實體化的記憶形象「連結卡」，裝備後能提升角色數值或是發動特殊能力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/WIKI/80/00363380.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FWIKI%2F80%2F00363380.JPG&h=806f20ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/WIKI/81/00363381.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FWIKI%2F81%2F00363381.JPG&h=cb63eb71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/WIKI/82/00363382.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FWIKI%2F82%2F00363382.JPG&h=1676b716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nios: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1446245280?l=ja&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1446245280%3Fl%3Dja%26ls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2VcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=c4613084\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1446245280?l=ja&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\nAn: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.plala.megamiracleforce\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.co.plala.megamiracleforce&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2VcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=80db18c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.plala.megamiracleforce</a>"},{"pid":"bafa250bedd977cef6efd172f9261c1c2d5e4f0a","tid":1005480,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"有冇海王星fans會玩下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然都係炒冷飯，但隻game勝在唔駛肝，可以輕鬆玩"},{"pid":"5c422e738cce70a52fef6d62be41e7e648ec4121","tid":1005480,"uid":155401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bafa250bedd977cef6efd172f9261c1c2d5e4f0a","tid":1005480,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"有冇海王星fans會玩下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然都係炒冷飯，但隻game勝在唔駛肝，可以輕鬆玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"啲點好難升。。"},{"pid":"4b26da87d638fe9d5ba3f44580aa0b